The Nigerian Independent Petroleum Company (NIPCO) has positioned its workforce for improved service delivery.
   
Managing Director and Chief Executive Officer of the company, Suresh Kumar, while addressing staff, thanked the employees for their resilience over the years, noting that the New Year offers a lot of opportunities, which must be optimised by the fuel marketing company.  “My charge to you all is that you should be ready for more challenges and responsibilities in 2022 because it is the sure pathway to our success in the New Year and even beyond,” he stated.